'''Mirai'''（{{lang-ja|ミライ}}<ref>{{Cite news|url= http://www.yomiuri.co.jp/national/20161029-OYT1T50069.html|title= IoT機器悪用、ウイルス「ミライ」世界で猛威|newspaper= YOUMIURI ONLINE|publisher= 読売新聞社|date= 2016-10-29|accessdate= 2016-10-31|archive-date= 2016-10-30|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20161030225126/http://www.yomiuri.co.jp/national/20161029-OYT1T50069.html|dead-url= yes}}</ref>，中文直譯「'''未來'''」<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/paper/1044757|title=美國網路遇駭 推特、亞馬遜遭殃|author=孫宇青|publisher=自由時報|date=2016-10-23|accessdate=2017-09-29|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807122215/https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/paper/1044757|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://technews.tw/2016/10/22/us-major-webs-down-by-hackers/|title=美主要網站遭駭客攻陷 升級國安層次|publisher=自由時報|date=2016-10-22|accessdate=2017-09-29|archive-date=2020-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201025110425/https://technews.tw/2016/10/22/us-major-webs-down-by-hackers/|dead-url=no}}</ref>）是一款[[恶意软件|恶意软件]]，它可以使运行[[Linux|Linux]]的计算系统成为被远程操控的“[[殭屍電腦|僵尸]]”，以达到通过[[僵尸网络|僵尸网络]]进行大规模网络攻击的目的。Mirai的主要感染对象是可访问网络的消费级电子设备，例如[[閉路電視|网络监控摄像机]]和[[路由器|家庭路由器]]等<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://techcrunch.com/2016/10/10/hackers-release-source-code-for-a-powerful-ddos-app-called-mirai/|title=Hackers release source code for a powerful DDoS app called Mirai|accessdate=2016-10-19|author=Biggs, John|date=2016-10-10|publisher=[[TechCrunch|TechCrunch]]|language=en|archive-date=2016-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161020105628/https://techcrunch.com/2016/10/10/hackers-release-source-code-for-a-powerful-ddos-app-called-mirai/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Mirai构建的僵尸网络已经参与了几次影响广泛的大型[[阻斷服務攻擊|分布式拒绝服务攻击]]（DDoS攻击），包括2016年9月20日针对计算机安全撰稿人{{link-en|布萊恩·克萊布斯|Brian Krebs}}个人网站的攻击、对法国网站托管商[[OVH|OVH]]的攻击<ref name="securityintelligence">{{Cite web|url=https://securityintelligence.com/news/leaked-mirai-malware-boosts-iot-insecurity-threat-level/|title=Leaked Mirai Malware Boosts IoT Insecurity Threat Level|accessdate=2016-10-20|author=Bonderud, Douglas|date=2016-10-04|publisher=securityintelligence.com|language=en|archive-date=2016-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161021003956/https://securityintelligence.com/news/leaked-mirai-malware-boosts-iot-insecurity-threat-level/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以及[[2016年10月Dyn公司遭到网络攻击事件|2016年10月Dyn公司网络攻击事件]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://fortune.com/2016/10/03/botnet-code-ddos-hacker/|title=Why a Hacker Dumped Code Behind Colossal Website-Trampling Botnet|accessdate=2016-10-19|author=Hackett, Robert|date=2016-10-03|publisher=[[Fortune_(magazine)|Fortune.com]]|language=en|archive-date=2016-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161022172232/http://fortune.com/2016/10/03/botnet-code-ddos-hacker/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="wired">{{Cite news|url=https://www.wired.com/2016/10/internet-outage-ddos-dns-dyn/|script-title=en:What We Know About Friday’s Massive East Coast Internet Outage|last=Newman|first=Lily Hay|newspaper=WIRED|accessdate=2016-10-21|language=en|archive-date=2016-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161022013504/https://www.wired.com/2016/10/internet-outage-ddos-dns-dyn/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/dyn#/entity|title=Dyn {{!}} crunchbase|accessdate=2016-10-23|language=en|archive-date=2019-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191226201551/https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/dyn#/entity|dead-url=no}}</ref>。目前已经确认上述攻击全部由Mirai作者构建的[[僵尸网络|僵尸网络]]发起的攻击。

Mirai的[[源代码|源代码]]已经以[[开源软件|开源]]的形式发布至黑客论坛<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.theverge.com/2016/10/21/13362354/dyn-dns-ddos-attack-cause-outage-status-explained|title=How an army of vulnerable gadgets took down the web today|accessdate=2016-10-21|date=2016-10-21|last=Statt|first=Nick|work=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|language=en|archive-date=2016-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161022013520/http://www.theverge.com/2016/10/21/13362354/dyn-dns-ddos-attack-cause-outage-status-explained|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其中的[[技术|技术]]也已被其他一些[[恶意软件|恶意软件]]采用<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.itworld.com/article/3132570/hackers-create-more-iot-botnets-with-mirai-source-code.html|title=Hackers create more IoT botnets with Mirai source code|accessdate=2016-10-20|author=Kan, Michael|date=2016-10-18|publisher=[[国际数据集团|ITWORLD]]|language=en|archive-date=2016-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161020025537/http://www.itworld.com/article/3132570/hackers-create-more-iot-botnets-with-mirai-source-code.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

根据一份泄露的软件作者之聊天记录，Mirai一名来自漫画改编的2011年[[日本动画|日本动画]]《[[未来日记|未来日记]]》<ref name="Krebs2017January">{{Cite web |url=https://krebsonsecurity.com/2017/01/who-is-anna-senpai-the-mirai-worm-author/ |title=Who is Anna-Senpai, the Mirai Worm Author? —  Krebs on Security |accessdate=2017-01-23 |work=krebsonsecurity.com |language=en |date=2017-01-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170122013744/https://krebsonsecurity.com/2017/01/who-is-anna-senpai-the-mirai-worm-author/ |archivedate=2017-01-22 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>；作者所用网名Anna-senpai（意为“安娜前辈”）则可能与日本輕小說《[[下流梗不存在的灰暗世界|-{zh-hant:下流梗不存在的灰暗世界;zh-cn:没有黄段子的无聊世界;}-]]》中的角色——[[下流梗不存在的灰暗世界#其他學生|安娜·锦之宫]]有关。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Heller |first1=Michael |title=Release of Mirai IoT botnet malware highlights bad password security |url=http://searchsecurity.techtarget.com/news/450400369/Release-of-Mirai-IoT-botnet-malware-highlights-bad-password-security |accessdate=2016-10-31 |publisher=TechTarget |date=2016-10-04 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20161031145711/http://searchsecurity.techtarget.com/news/450400369/Release-of-Mirai-IoT-botnet-malware-highlights-bad-password-security |archivedate=2016-10-31 |language=en |quote=Both names Anna and Mirai reference Japanese anime. |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Cox|first1=Edward|title=Mirai IoT Botnet: 5 Fast Facts You Need to Know|url=http://heavy.com/tech/2016/10/mirai-iot-botnet-internet-of-things-ddos-attacks-internet-outage-blackout-why-is-internet-down/|accessdate=2016-10-31|publisher=Heavy.com|date=2016-10-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161022163144/http://heavy.com/tech/2016/10/mirai-iot-botnet-internet-of-things-ddos-attacks-internet-outage-blackout-why-is-internet-down/|archivedate=2016-10-22|language=en|quote={{lang|en|3. ‘Mirai’s Author Has an Avi of Anime Character Anna Nishikinomiya and Mirai Means “Future” in Japanese}}|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 行为 ==
受Mirai感染的设备会持续地在互联网上扫描[[物联网|物联网]]设备的[[IP地址|IP地址]]。Mirai包含一张IP白名单表，其中包括[[专用网络|专用网络]]的私有IP地址以及分配给[[美國郵政署|美国邮政署]]和[[美国国防部|美国国防部]]的IP地址，使用这些地址的设备将不会受Mirai感染。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.incapsula.com/blog/malware-analysis-mirai-ddos-botnet.html|title=Breaking Down Mirai: An IoT DDoS Botnet Analysis|accessdate=2016-10-20|author=Zeifman, Igal|date=2016-10-10|publisher={{tsl|en|Incapsula}}|language=en|archive-date=2016-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161021075900/https://www.incapsula.com/blog/malware-analysis-mirai-ddos-botnet.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在扫描到IP地址之后，Mirai会通过超过60种常用默认用户名和密码辨别出易受攻击的设备，然后登录这些设备以注入Mirai软件<ref name="webroot">{{Cite web|url=https://www.webroot.com/blog/2016/10/10/source-code-mirai-iot-malware-released/|title=Source Code for Mirai IoT Malware Released|accessdate=2016-10-20|author=Moffitt, Tyler|date=2016-10-10|publisher={{tsl|en|Webroot}}|language=en|archive-date=2016-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161021064505/https://www.webroot.com/blog/2016/10/10/source-code-mirai-iot-malware-released/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="securityintelligence"/><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.zdnet.com/article/mirai-ddos-botnet-powers-up-infects-sierra-wireless-gateways/|title=Mirai DDoS botnet powers up, infects Sierra Wireless gateways|accessdate=2016-10-20|author=Osborne, Charlie|date=2016-10-17|publisher=[[ZDNet|ZDNet]]|language=en|archive-date=2016-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161020045727/http://www.zdnet.com/article/mirai-ddos-botnet-powers-up-infects-sierra-wireless-gateways/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。受感染的设备会继续正常工作，不过偶尔会出现卡顿，而且[[带宽|带宽]]消耗会增大<ref name="webroot"/>。设备在重新启动之前将一直保持受感染的状态。设备重启之后，除非用户立刻修改密码，几分钟之内设备很快会被再次感染<ref name="webroot"/>。Mirai还会在成功感染后删除设备上的同类恶意软件，并屏蔽用于远程管理的端口<ref>{{cite web | url=https://servercomparator.com/vpn/blog/dyn-mirai-ddos-complete-story | title=DDoS on Dyn The Complete Story | publisher=ServerComparator | date=2016-10-28 | accessdate=2016-11-21 | author=Xander | language=en | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161121175123/https://servercomparator.com/vpn/blog/dyn-mirai-ddos-complete-story | archivedate=2016-11-21 }}</ref>。

互联网上有成千上万的物联网设备使用默认设置，这些设备都很容易受到感染。受感染的设备会监视一台下发{{tsl|en|Command and control (malware)|命令与控制 (恶意软件)|命令与控制}}的服务器，该服务器将指示发起攻击的目标。<ref name="webroot"/>

== 在DDoS攻击中的使用 ==
2016年9月20日，攻击者通过Mirai和{{tsl|en|BASHLITE}}<ref name="arstechnica.com">{{cite web|url=http://arstechnica.com/security/2016/10/double-dip-internet-of-things-botnet-attack-felt-across-the-internet/|title=Double-dip Internet-of-Things botnet attack felt across the Internet|publisher=|language=en|accessdate=2017-01-23|archive-date=2017-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170519112613/https://arstechnica.com/security/2016/10/double-dip-internet-of-things-botnet-attack-felt-across-the-internet/|dead-url=no}}</ref>对{{tsl|en|Krebs on Security}}网站发动了[[DDoS|DDoS攻击]]，攻击流量达到了620 Gbps<ref>{{cite web|title=The internet of stings|url=http://www.economist.com/news/science-and-technology/21708220-electronic-tsunami-crashes-down-solitary-journalist-internet|website=经济学人|accessdate=2016-10-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161017161220/http://www.economist.com/news/science-and-technology/21708220-electronic-tsunami-crashes-down-solitary-journalist-internet|archivedate=2016-10-17|language=en|date=2016-10-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]报道称在对法国网站托管商[[OVH|OVH]]的攻击中发现了1 Tbps的攻击流量<ref name="securityintelligence"/>。

2016年10月21日，{{tsl|en|Dyn (company)|Dyn (公司)|Dyn}}公司提供的[[DNS|DNS]]服务遭到了数次通过Mirai发起的大型DDoS攻击，牵涉到的受感染[[物联网|物联网设备]]数量众多。这次攻击使得数个高访问量的网站无法正常打开，其中包括[[GitHub|GitHub]]、[[Twitter|Twitter]]、[[Reddit|Reddit]]、[[Netflix|Netflix]]和[[Airbnb|Airbnb]]等<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.theregister.co.uk/2016/10/21/dyn_dns_ddos_explained/|title=Today the web was broken by countless hacked devices|accessdate=2016-10-24|date=2016-10-21|publisher=theregister.co.uk|language=en|archive-date=2020-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200517021807/https://www.theregister.co.uk/2016/10/21/dyn_dns_ddos_explained/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Mirai和这次攻击的关联最初是由[[Level_3_通信|Level 3 通信]]在报告中指出的<ref name="arstechnica.com" /><ref>{{cite web|title=Blame the Internet of Things for Destroying the Internet Today|url=http://motherboard.vice.com/read/blame-the-internet-of-things-for-destroying-the-internet-today|website=Motherboard|publisher=VICE|accessdate=27 October 2016|archive-date=2016-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161024221854/http://motherboard.vice.com/read/blame-the-internet-of-things-for-destroying-the-internet-today|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

有[[深度学习|深度学习]]方面的安全专家发现，Mirai构建的僵尸网络数量在Dyn攻击事件发生前后有稳定的上升。<ref>{{cite web |author1=Deep Learning Security |script-title=en:Think Mirai DDoS is over? It ain’t!! |url=https://medium.com/@deeplearningsec/think-mirai-ddos-is-over-it-aint-96298a9ff896 |website=Medium |accessdate=2016-10-27 |archiveurl=https://archive.fo/20161027065817/https://medium.com/@deeplearningsec/think-mirai-ddos-is-over-it-aint-96298a9ff896 |archivedate=2016-10-27 |language=en |date=2016-10-26 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

Mirai亦被用于2016年11月针对[[利比里亚|利比里亚]]互联网基础设施的攻击<ref name="tel1">{{cite web|title=Unprecedented cyber attack takes Liberia's entire internet down|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/2016/11/04/unprecedented-cyber-attack-takes-liberias-entire-internet-down/|publisher=The Telegraph|accessdate=2016-11-21|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126020030/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/2016/11/04/unprecedented-cyber-attack-takes-liberias-entire-internet-down/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=DDoS attack from Mirai malware 'killing business' in Liberia|url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/3138631/security/ddos-attack-from-mirai-malware-killing-business-in-liberia.html|publisher=PCWorld|accessdate=2016-11-21|language=en|archive-date=2016-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161122072327/http://www.pcworld.com/article/3138631/security/ddos-attack-from-mirai-malware-killing-business-in-liberia.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Massive cyber-attack grinds Liberia's internet to a halt|url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2016/nov/03/cyberattack-internet-liberia-ddos-hack-botnet|publisher=The Guardian|accessdate=2016-11-21|language=en|archive-date=2016-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161121103649/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2016/nov/03/cyberattack-internet-liberia-ddos-hack-botnet|dead-url=no}}</ref>。计算机安全专家Kevin Beaumont认为这次攻击的发动者与Dyn攻击相同<ref name="tel1" />。

== 其他事件 ==
2016年11月末，90万台[[德国电信|德国电信]]用户的[[路由器|路由器]]因Mirai变种利用TR-064协议的一次失败尝试而崩溃，这些路由器由智易科技生产，受影响用户的互联网访问因此出现异常<ref>{{cite web | url=https://krebsonsecurity.com/2016/11/new-mirai-worm-knocks-900k-germans-offline/ | title=New Mirai Worm Knocks 900K Germans Offline | publisher=krebsonsecurity.com | date=2016-11-30 | accessdate=2016-12-14 | author=Krebs, Brian | language=en | archive-date=2016-12-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220161008/https://krebsonsecurity.com/2016/11/new-mirai-worm-knocks-900k-germans-offline/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=German leaders angry at cyberattack, hint at Russian involvement {{!}} Germany {{!}} DW.COM {{!}} 29.11.2016|url=http://www.dw.com/en/german-leaders-angry-at-cyberattack-hint-at-russian-involvement/a-36573668|publisher=Deutsche Welle|accessdate=2017-01-05|language=en|archive-date=2017-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170105181243/http://www.dw.com/en/german-leaders-angry-at-cyberattack-hint-at-russian-involvement/a-36573668|dead-url=no}}</ref>。尽管另一家名为TalkTalk的运营商随后更新了他们的路由器，但仍有TalkTalk路由器感染上Mirai的另一支新变种<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.incapsula.com/blog/new-variant-mirai-embeds-talktalk-home-routers.html|title=New Mirai Variant Embeds in TalkTalk Home Routers|website=www.incapsula.com|access-date=2016-12-18|language=en|archive-date=2016-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222032237/https://www.incapsula.com/blog/new-variant-mirai-embeds-talktalk-home-routers.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 作者 ==
Krebs on Security网站在2017年1月发布报告，认为Mirai的作者“Anna-senpai”真名为Paras Jha，是[[罗格斯大学|罗格斯大学]]学生和一家DDoS防御服务提供商总裁<ref name="Krebs2017January" /><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://social.techcrunch.com/2017/01/18/mirai-botnet-creator-unmasked-as-ddos-protection-developer-tempted-by-the-dark-side/ |title=Mirai botnet creator unmasked as DDOS protection developer tempted by the dark side |accessdate=2017-01-23 |last=Coldewey |first=Devin |work=TechCrunch |date=2017-01-18 |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170123044733/https://techcrunch.com/2017/01/18/mirai-botnet-creator-unmasked-as-ddos-protection-developer-tempted-by-the-dark-side/ |archivedate=2017-01-23 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，但后者否认这一指控的真实性<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.solidot.org/story?sid=51153 |title=Solidot {{!}} Krebs 找到 Mirai 僵尸网络可能的作者 |accessdate=2017-01-23 |work=www.solidot.org |date=2017-01-20 |language=zh-hans |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170123082127/http://www.solidot.org/story?sid=51153 |archivedate=2017-01-23 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。[[美国联邦调查局|美国联邦调查局]]之后对其进行了盘问<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.nj.com/news/index.ssf/2017/01/rutgers_student_questioned_cyber_attack.html |title=FBI questions Rutgers student about massive cyber attack |newspaper=NJ.com |accessdate=2017-01-23 |language=en |date=2017-01-20 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20170123081123/http://www.nj.com/news/index.ssf/2017/01/rutgers_student_questioned_cyber_attack.html |archivedate=2017-01-23 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

2017年12月10日美国联邦调查局已经公布调查结果，而在此之前Mirai的作者已经被捕。该作者确实就是此前Krebs on Security研究人员认为的Paras Jha<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.landiannews.com/archives/43482.html|title=针对物联网设备的蠕虫病毒Mirai开发者已经被捕|accessdate=2017-12-15|author=|date=|publisher=|archive-date=2020-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813121533/https://www.landiannews.com/archives/43482.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

